{
  "_comment": [
    "ComfyUI API-format workflow for FramePack long image-to-video generation.",
    "",
    "Node class_types sourced from:",
    "  FramePackWrapper nodes.py NODE_CLASS_MAPPINGS (kijai/ComfyUI-FramePackWrapper, HEAD a0eeaa6993e8)",
    "  ComfyUI nodes.py NODE_CLASS_MAPPINGS (comfyanonymous/ComfyUI, master 2025-04)",
    "  ComfyUI-VideoHelperSuite nodes.py NODE_CLASS_MAPPINGS (Kosinkadink, HEAD 2984ec4c4b93)",
    "",
    "Data-flow summary:",
    "  [DualCLIPLoader] ──────────┐",
    "  [CLIPTextEncode pos/neg] ──┼──> [FramePackSampler] -> [VAEDecode] -> [VHS_VideoCombine]",
    "  [LoadFramePackModel] ───────┘                ↑",
    "  [LoadImage] -> [FramePackFindNearestBucket] -> [VAEEncode (start_latent)]",
    "  [CLIPVisionLoader] -> [CLIPVisionEncode] ────────────> (image_embeds)",
    "  [VAELoader] ─────────────────────────────────────────> (vae)",
    "",
    "The remote driver patches these fields by _meta.title before submitting:",
    "  'Input Keyframe'        -> inputs.image",
    "  'Positive Prompt'       -> inputs.text",
    "  'Negative Prompt'       -> inputs.text",
    "  'FramePack Sampler'     -> inputs.total_second_length, seed"
  ],
  "1": {
    "class_type": "LoadFramePackModel",
    "_meta": { "title": "Load FramePack Model" },
    "inputs": {
      "model": "FramePackI2V_HY_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors",
      "base_precision": "fp8_e4m3fn",
      "quantization": "disabled",
      "attention_mode": "sdpa"
    }
  },
  "2": {
    "class_type": "DualCLIPLoader",
    "_meta": { "title": "Dual CLIP Loader (HunyuanVideo)" },
    "inputs": {
      "clip_name1": "llava_llama3_fp8_scaled.safetensors",
      "clip_name2": "clip_l.safetensors",
      "type": "hunyuan_video"
    }
  },
  "3": {
    "class_type": "CLIPTextEncode",
    "_meta": { "title": "Positive Prompt" },
    "inputs": {
      "text": "PLACEHOLDER_POS",
      "clip": ["2", 0]
    }
  },
  "4": {
    "class_type": "CLIPTextEncode",
    "_meta": { "title": "Negative Prompt" },
    "inputs": {
      "text": "PLACEHOLDER_NEG",
      "clip": ["2", 0]
    }
  },
  "5": {
    "class_type": "VAELoader",
    "_meta": { "title": "Load VAE" },
    "inputs": {
      "vae_name": "hunyuan_video_vae_bf16.safetensors"
    }
  },
  "6": {
    "class_type": "CLIPVisionLoader",
    "_meta": { "title": "Load CLIP Vision (SigCLIP)" },
    "inputs": {
      "clip_name": "sigclip_vision_patch14_384.safetensors"
    }
  },
  "7": {
    "class_type": "LoadImage",
    "_meta": { "title": "Input Keyframe" },
    "inputs": {
      "image": "input_keyframe.png",
      "upload": "image"
    }
  },
  "8": {
    "class_type": "FramePackFindNearestBucket",
    "_meta": { "title": "FramePack Find Nearest Bucket" },
    "inputs": {
      "image": ["7", 0],
      "width": 768,
      "height": 432,
      "interpolation": "nearest"
    }
  },
  "9": {
    "class_type": "VAEEncode",
    "_meta": { "title": "VAE Encode (Start Latent)" },
    "inputs": {
      "pixels": ["8", 0],
      "vae": ["5", 0]
    }
  },
  "10": {
    "class_type": "CLIPVisionEncode",
    "_meta": { "title": "Encode Image Embeds (SigCLIP)" },
    "inputs": {
      "clip_vision": ["6", 0],
      "image": ["8", 0],
      "crop": "center"
    }
  },
  "11": {
    "class_type": "FramePackSampler",
    "_meta": { "title": "FramePack Sampler" },
    "inputs": {
      "model":                  ["1", 0],
      "positive":               ["3", 0],
      "negative":               ["4", 0],
      "start_latent":           ["9", 0],
      "image_embeds":           ["10", 0],
      "steps":                  25,
      "use_teacache":           true,
      "teacache_rel_l1_thresh": 0.15,
      "cfg":                    7.0,
      "guidance_scale":         10.0,
      "shift":                  0.0,
      "seed":                   42,
      "latent_window_size":     9,
      "total_second_length":    10.0,
      "gpu_memory_preservation": 6.0,
      "sampler":                "unipc_bh1"
    }
  },
  "12": {
    "class_type": "VAEDecode",
    "_meta": { "title": "VAE Decode" },
    "inputs": {
      "samples": ["11", 0],
      "vae":     ["5", 0]
    }
  },
  "13": {
    "class_type": "VHS_VideoCombine",
    "_meta": { "title": "Video Combine (MP4 Output)" },
    "inputs": {
      "images":          ["12", 0],
      "frame_rate":      24,
      "loop_count":      0,
      "filename_prefix": "framepack/output",
      "format":          "video/h264-mp4",
      "pingpong":        false,
      "save_output":     true
    }
  }
}
